This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it presents a large-scale visual object detection and tracking benchmark. The paper also mentions the use of deep learning techniques for visual analysis on drone platforms, which falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The paper also discusses the challenges of tracking objects in fast motion, which is a topic in robotics (cs.RO). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning algorithms for visual analysis, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Finally, the paper presents a dataset of images and videos, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
